one time in sixth grade, which was 2001, a classmate called me “Heyyy ben Laden!” 

So I, wanting to make a friend, shouted back “YUP THATS ME, BEN LADEN,” and my teacher immediately made ONLY ME write a 2 page paper on how dangerous he was to America.
